		      <td colspan="2" class="text"><p class="bold">Summer Work Travel Program &ndash; At a glance</p>
		        <p>CSB has been designed by the United States Department of State to administer the Summer Work Travel Program.  The program is designed to allow foreign university students the opportunity to live, work and travel in the United States for a maximum period of 4 months, but within the limits of the official annual summer vacation. </p>
		        <p>The students have the privilege to experience life in the United States in a unique and dynamic way: by sharing its tradition and culture through short-term work opportunities, an experience very different from that of a tourist. At the end of the program, all participants can enjoy an additional month for exploring the United States. What an exciting way to spend the summer abroad!</p>
		        <p><span class="bold">Next summer vacation in the United States?</span> Click here for more program information.</p>
